# NB: do NOT add `data/` here — it ships runtime YAML files
# (clothing_ontology.yaml, color_dimensions.yaml, outfit_templates.yaml)
# read by app.services.wardrobe.attribute_normalizer and
# app.services.outfits.outfit_generator. Excluding the folder makes the
# prod image build fine but every /wardrobe/upload returns 500 —
# attribute normalization can't find its ontology file.
